<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-20699] Fix SAI virtual table names</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20699</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SAI virtual table &quot;system_views.indexes&quot; was renamed to &quot;system_views.sai_column_indexes&quot; in this commit:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/e5e0f3a8441503107b1ca2128cf8366e5e44d893&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/e5e0f3a8441503107b1ca2128cf8366e5e44d893&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And also correct table names for these tables are:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;system_views.sstable_indexes -&amp;gt; system_views.sai_sstable_indexes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;system_views.sstable_index_segments -&amp;gt; system_views.sai_sstable_index_segments&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Therefore, documents on these pages need to change:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/reference/sai-virtual-table-indexes.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/reference/sai-virtual-table-indexes.html&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/indexing/sai/sai-faq.html#when-i-drop-and-recreate-an-sai-index-on-the-same-column-does-that-block-any-read-operations-and-is-there-a-way-to-check-the-indexing-status&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/indexing/sai/sai-faq.html#when-i-drop-and-recreate-an-sai-index-on-the-same-column-does-that-block-any-read-operations-and-is-there-a-way-to-check-the-indexing-status&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/indexing/sai/operations/monitoring.html#saiMonitorVirtualTables&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/indexing/sai/operations/monitoring.html#saiMonitorVirtualTables&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are also other minor issues with &quot;sai-virtual-table-indexes&quot; file:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Columns &quot;cell_count, indexed_sstable_count, per_column_disk_size, per_table_disk_size&quot; do not exist in &quot;system_views.sai_column_indexes&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Invalid reference to &quot;SAI information&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&quot;component_metadata&quot; field type is different in &quot;system_views.sai_sstable_index_segments&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
